text: Super High Me is a 2007 American documentary movie. It is directed by Michael Blieden. It stars comedian Doug Benson. In the documentary, Benson smokes cannabis for 30 days straight to see the effects. The title of Super High Me and its poster are plays on the documentary Super Size Me (2004) by Morgan Spurlock. Super High Me had its full release on April 20, 2008 (4/20).
